-- ECB BULLETIN-ECB issues monthly bulletin
-- 
-- Thu Dec 11, 2014 04:04AM EST
-- None



FRANKFURT, Dec 11 (Reuters) - The European Central Bank is ready to step up its stimulus should inflation in the euro zone remain too low for too long, it reiterated on Thursday in its monthly bulletin.

